articles.title: Jofra Archer signs new contract extension at Sussex - Sussex Cricket
articles.description: Sussex Cricket is delighted to announce that England international fast-bowler Jofra Archer has signed a contract extension with the Club. Archer, who has been with Sussex since 2016, took 181 first-class wickets for the Club, before becoming one of England's…
